<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#A0A1A7;--shiki-light-font-style:italic;--shiki-dark:#7F848E;--shiki-dark-font-style:italic"># 手动设置一个密码,`NEW_PASSWORD`是指你需要设置的密码</span></span>
